============================================================
CURRENT STATUS — EXCLUDED FROM BUILD
============================================================

This GPL v2 code has been completely excluded from the Octo iOS build
via WuKongBase.podspec's `exclude_files`. Source files are retained in
the repository solely to preserve the GPL v2 attribution required by
sections 4(b) and 4(d) of the license.

All four external consumer components have been replaced with native
UIKit / CoreGraphics implementations during the P5 phase:

  ContextExtractedContentContainingNode → WKContentContainerNode
  ContextControllerSourceNode           → WKGestureContainerNode
  RadialStatusNode                      → WKRadialProgressView
  StickerShimmerEffectNode              → WKShimmerView
  GradientBackgroundNode (preview)      → CoreGraphics CGGradient
  ContextController (long-press menu)   → custom showInlineMenuForCell

See README.md in this directory for details.

If a future change re-introduces a build-time dependency on any file
in this directory, the project will lose its Apache 2.0 license clarity
and revert to a GPL v2 obligation. Please open an issue first.

